The '''2010 edition''' of the '''[[K-League]]''' is the twenty-eighth since its establishment in 1983. The 2010 season is known as ''Sonata K-League 2010'' due to the competition's sponsorship by [[Hyundai Motor Company]]. [[Jeonbuk Hyundai Motors]] is the defending champions, having won their first title. The season began on 27 February 2010. The [[2010_K-League_Championship|final match]] was played on 5 December 2010.

