==Awards==
===K-League Most Valuable Player===
*The [[K-League Most Valuable Player]] award was won by [[Kim Eun-Jung]] ([[Jeju United FC]])

===K-League Rookie of the Year===
*The [[K-League Rookie of the Year]] award was won by [[Yoon Bit-Garam]] ([[Gyeongnam FC]])

===K-League Top Scorer===
*The [[K-League Top Scorer]] award was won by [[Yoo Byung-Soo]] ([[Incheon United FC]])

===K-League Top Assistor===
*The [[K-League Top Assistor]] award was won by [[Koo Ja-Cheol]] ([[Jeju United FC]])

