===K-League Manager of the Year===
*The [[K-League Manager of the Year]] award was won by [[Park Kyung-Hoon]] ([[Jeju United FC]])

===K-League Team of the Year===
*The K-League Team of the Year award was won by [[FC Seoul]]

===K-League Youth Team of the Year===
*The K-League Team of the Year award was won by [[Suwon Samsung Bluewings|Maetan High School (Suwon Samsung Bluewings Youth)]]

===K-League Fair Play Award===
*The K-League Fair Play award was won by [[Gangwon FC]]

===K-League Special Award===
*[[FC Seoul]] goalkeeper [[Kim Yong-Dae]], [[Gyeongnam FC|Gyeongnam]] goalkeeper [[Kim Byung-Ji]] and [[Daegu FC]] goalkeeper [[Baek Min-Cheol]] won the Special award

==='FAN'tastic Player===
The [[K-League 'FAN'tastic Player]] was won by [[Koo Ja-Cheol]] ([[Jeju United FC]])

